#
# component: smartXsensIMUMTiServer
#

A) DEPENDENCIES
   ------------

   - MRPT library
   - ncurses


B) PREPARATIONS
   ------------
   
   - Download and install the MRPT library
     (Version used to develop this component: V0.6.5)
     http://www.mrpt.org
   - Specify the path to the mrpt-config folder in the Makefile (line 39)

     DO NOT CHANGE ANYTHING ELSE IN THE MAKEFILE UNTIL YOU ARE REALLY 
     SURE ABOUT WHAT YOU ARE DOING!


C) COMPILE
   -------

   <make>: compiles the component

   other targets:

    <clean>
    <distclean>


